&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Target Machine IP:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;10.162.21.133&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The objective was to enumerate the target, identify exposed services, gain initial access, and escalate privileges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://nvru.github.io/images/hmv/helix/vm.png&#34; alt=&#34;Machine information&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
